title: I didin't get my season rewards :(
body: I have finished season 6 with a silver IV rank and I didin't recive any season rewards.  :(

replies.body:
There were [some issues](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) with certain players getting ranked rewards. We're looking into this, so I recommend [submitting a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can assist you with this.

Let me know if you have any questions.
ok ty I have submitted a ticket :)
